) provides:

The foregoing provisions have been reproduced in identical form in Council Regulation (EU) 2015/1589 of 13 July 2015 laying down detailed rules for the application of Article 108 of the Treaty on the Functioning of the European Union (
OJ 2015 L 248, p. 9
).

